        "TileImage": "$($repository 3f808b28-3647-44f3-9aeb-4d5ae6d63573).Image",
        "Description": "Alright, let&apos;s see your form, Mr. Rieper... Security detail, I see.\r\rWell, you can probably take Frank&apos;s uniform. He&apos;s not gonna need it for much longer, it&apos;s his last day. Mind the pit stains.\r\rAnd your first job as security detail here at Milton-Fitzpatrick is surveillance duty. You may speak and learn from our heads of security on multiple floors.\r\rWhat&apos;s that? You think you can do better. Yeah, I&apos;d like to see you try.",
